Class Summary

DmcTypeFloat The DmcFloat type is meant to store Float values.
DmcTypeInteger The DmcInteger type is meant to store Integer values.
DmcTypeLong The DmcLong type is meant to store Long values.
DmcTypeNamedObjectREF<HELPER extends DmcNamedObjectREF> The DmcTypeNamedObjectREF is a base type from which all references to named objects are derived.
